{
  "texts": [
    "Importantly, each stage also provides a leverage point for ethical counter-action.",
    "The very tools exploited to scale disinformation -such as generative models or bot frameworkscan be repurposed for detection, simulation, and remediation.",
    "For instance, adversarial testing using synthetic bots helps platforms stress-test moderation filters, while generative models are used to train classifiers to recognize manipulated content.",
    "In the evolving contest between disinformation and truth, AI is both a weapon and a shield.",
    "Its deployment must be grounded in an understanding that harm stems not from the existence of a tool, but from its application and the ecosystem of incentives surrounding it."
  ]
}